news.title: JMC-Greater deputy mayor raises issue of Rs 400 crore dues from Rajasthan housing board
news.para: The RHB on Monday gave an amount of Rs 23.23 crore to JMC-Greater for development works. This is the first time in 15 years, that the RHB gave the 15% of its earnings to JMC-Greater, as stated in the provisions.

news.title: North East governments rush to meet new PMAY-Gramin deadline
news.para: Sadhvi Niranjan Jyoti informed while about 85% of the 2.49 crore houses sanctioned by various states and Union territories under PMAY-G scheme have been completed nationally, 50% to 80% of the sanctioned houses remain incomplete in the northeast.

news.title: No stamp duty when family member forgoes rights: Gujarat HC
news.para: According to the case details, Mukesh Patel bought 51 hectares of land in Zundal in 2000, and got it converted to non-agricultural land.

news.title: Haryana government to waive interest on pending property tax till Dec 31
news.para: ​With an estimated Rs 1,000 crore outstanding payment, property owners or occupiers have been asked to deposit the tax before December 31, 2022, under the House Tax Interest Waiver Scheme implemented by the government in urban areas.

news.title: DDA to hold draw of lots for waitlisted applicants under housing scheme 2021 on Dec 15
news.para: ​The draw will be based on random number generation system and will be held in the presence of independent observers comprising a retired judge and senior officers of the central government, the DDA said in a statement.

news.title: Decide on Jaypee resolution plan by January 16: Allahabad HC to buyers
news.para: During a hearing a two-judge bench was informed by the YEIDA counsel that the Authority had taken a decision on the proposal of the petitioner (JAL) and it would bring the same on record by means of an affidavit after serving its copy on all the parties within three days.

news.title: Noida authority links OCs to compulsory facade lights for e-way buildings
news.para: To begin with, it has dispatched letters to 40 developers of completed real estate, which includes both residential and commercial buildings, setting a four-month deadline to put up facade lights.

news.title: Sanskar Homes buys south Delhi property for Rs 71 crore
news.para: Earlier the company, which focuses on luxury floors, had acquired a bungalow from Mobius Foundation chairman Pradip Burman for about Rs 75 crore.

news.title: China's Guangzhou R&F co-chief accused of bribery in U.S., London court hears
news.para: Zhang Li, who co-founded Hong Kong-listed R&F, is wanted on a provisional warrant issued in the Northern District of California that accuses him of participating in a scheme to bribe public officials between 2015 and 2020.

news.title: Bullish on India, to add Rs 2,500-crore projects in one year, says Trump Jr
news.para: The Trump Organisation will be ramping up its portfolio here through its India partner Tribeca Developers, which itself is looking to add projects worth Rs 5,000 crore, including its Trump branded portfolio, in 2023.

news.title: WeWork India expects to clock revenue of Rs 1,500 crore in FY23: CEO
news.para: The firm clocked 250% growth in earnings before interest, taxes, depreciation and amortisation (EBIDTA) registering Rs 175 crore profit in 2022, as against a loss of Rs 120 crore last calendar year.

news.title: All residential & commercial properties to get unique digital door number in Jammu
news.para: The mapping of the residential and commercial properties would enable the citizens to avail maximum benefits of civic services as well as governance, the official said.

news.title: TARC prepays Rs 66 crore towards non-convertible debentures
news.para: BAIN Capital USA has invested by way of non-convertible debentures (NCDs) Rs 1,330 crore on April 29, 2022.

news.title: Rajasthan housing board gives Rs 23 crore to JMC-Greater for development work
news.para: ​This is for the first time in 15 years that the housing board gave 15% of its earnings to JMC-Greater, as stated in the provisions. The amount paid is for the financial year 2010-11 till 2021-22.

news.title: Master plan of three more cities up for government approval in Uttar Pradesh
news.para: The three cities where fresh focus has been made on spatial planning, public health facilities, water supply, urban transportation and socio-economic development through the master plan 2031 are Kanpur, Azamgarh and Hapur.
